Egypt to Issue Saudi Power-Link Tender in Mid-April, Younes Says

-- B y   O l a   G a l a l
-- 
2011-03-28T10:57:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/egypt-to-issue-saudi-power-link-tender-in-mid-april-younes-says.html
Egypt  plans to issue a tender in
mid-April for the construction of a  power grid  linking the north
African country to  Saudi Arabia , Egyptian Electricity Minister
Hassan Younes said.  Saudi Electricity Co. and Egyptian Electricity Holding Co.
will each finance, own, operate and maintain that part of the
grid in their respective countries while dividing equally the
cost of the underwater segment, Younes said today in a statement
